<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="/img/Logo-Icon.png" type="image/png">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="ambient-gradient"></div>
  <div class="ambient-diagonal"></div>

  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <section class="landing-hero">
    <p class="arm-eyebrow">ACED Pixels · Creative & Visual</p>
    <h1>Visual Systems Built to<br>Make You Impossible to Ignore.</h1>
    <p>Brand identity, photography, cinematography, graphic design, and conversion-focused visual systems — crafted to give your audience something they can't scroll past.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="#services" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Services</a>
      <a href="#portfolio" class="btn btn-secondary">See Creative Work</a>
      <a href="mailto:support@aceddivision.com" class="btn btn-accent">Start a Project</a>
    </div>
    <div class="capability-strip">
      <div class="capability-strip-inner">
        <span>BRAND IDENTITY</span><span>·</span>
        <span>PHOTOGRAPHY</span><span>·</span>
        <span>CINEMATOGRAPHY</span><span>·</span>
        <span>GRAPHIC DESIGN</span><span>·</span>
        <span>WEB DESIGN</span><span>·</span>
        <span>MOTION GRAPHICS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>VFX & ANIMATION</span><span>·</span>
        <span>BRAND IDENTITY</span><span>·</span>
        <span>PHOTOGRAPHY</span><span>·</span>
        <span>CINEMATOGRAPHY</span><span>·</span>
        <span>GRAPHIC DESIGN</span><span>·</span>
        <span>WEB DESIGN</span><span>·</span>
        <span>MOTION GRAPHICS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>VFX & ANIMATION</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="trust-strip">
    <div class="trust-item">
      <h3>Multi-Platform Creative</h3>
      <p>Print, digital, web, and motion — one cohesive creative language</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <h3>Brand-First Thinking</h3>
      <p>Every visual decision is rooted in your identity and audience</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <h3>Conversion-Focused Design</h3>
      <p>Beautiful design that actually moves people to act</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="numbered-list" id="services">
    <h2>Four things every brand knows too well.</h2>
    <div class="numbered-items">
      <div class="numbered-item">
        <span class="numbered-item-num">01</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Looking smaller than you are</h3>
          <p>Poor visuals signal under-investment. Even solid businesses lose trust when their brand looks inconsistent or amateurish across channels.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="numbered-item">
        <span class="numbered-item-num">02</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Creative that never quite captures the vision</h3>
          <p>Designers who don't understand your business produce beautiful deliverables that miss the point entirely. Vision requires partnership, not just skill.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="numbered-item">
        <span class="numbered-item-num">03</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Visual fragmentation across touchpoints</h3>
          <p>When the Instagram post, website, and deck look like three different brands, the cumulative effect is distrust — even when it's unintended.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="numbered-item">
        <span class="numbered-item-num">04</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Visuals that don't convert</h3>
          <p>Creative work that isn't built around conversion objectives is art, not execution. The two aren't mutually exclusive — you need both.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section" style="padding-top:0;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom:2rem;">Capabilities built for brand impact.</h2>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>📸 Photography</h3>
        <p>Professional photography capturing your brand, team, and products with precision and artistic vision — ready for web, print, and social.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>🎥 Cinematography & Video</h3>
        <p>High-quality video production and post-production services that tell your brand story with cinematic excellence and technical precision.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>🎨 Graphic Design</h3>
        <p>Custom design solutions including marketing materials, digital assets, pitch decks, and visual content that commands attention.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>🖼️ Brand Identity</h3>
        <p>Complete branding — logo, colour systems, typography, and guidelines — creating a cohesive visual identity that carries across every medium.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>🌐 Web Design</h3>
        <p>Conversion-focused, visually elevated web experiences that balance beautiful design with clear user journeys and measurable outcomes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>✨ Motion & VFX</h3>
        <p>Visual effects and animation adding dynamic energy and professional polish to any visual communication — from social cuts to full productions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <% if (featuredProjects && featuredProjects.length > 0) { %>
  <section class="showcase" id="portfolio">
    <div class="max-w-container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Selected Work</p>
      <h2>Creative Portfolio</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Visual systems, web platforms, and brand experiences delivered across a range of industries and creative objectives.</p>
      <div class="showcase-grid">
        <% featuredProjects.forEach((project) => { %>
          <article class="showcase-card">
            <h3><%= project.title %></h3>
            <p><%= project.description %></p>
            <div class="chip-row">
              <% (project.tags || []).slice(0, 3).forEach((tag) => { %><span><%= tag %></span><% }) %>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:1rem;">
              <a href="/portfolio/<%= project.slug %>">View case study →</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-buttons" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <a href="/portfolio?arm=pixels" class="btn btn-secondary">View All Creative Work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <% } %>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="features-content">
      <h2>Creative Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3>✦ Brand-Rooted Visuals</h3>
          <p>Every creative decision traces back to your identity, your audience, and the feeling you want to create in a room.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3>✦ Cross-Platform Cohesion</h3>
          <p>Digital, print, web, motion — one unified creative language that makes your brand recognisable everywhere it appears.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3>✦ Conversion-Aware Design</h3>
          <p>We build visuals that earn attention and guide people toward action — not just things that look good on a screen.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3>✦ Directorial Eye</h3>
          <p>Every frame, layout, and composition is intentional. Production quality that positions you as the credible option.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-section" id="contact">
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div>
        <p class="arm-eyebrow">ACED Pixels</p>
        <h2>Your brand deserves visuals that actually work.</h2>
        <p>Tell us about your project — brand, campaign, web, or video — and we'll come back with a clear creative plan.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-actions">
        <a href="mailto:support@aceddivision.com" class="btn btn-accent">support@aceddivision.com</a>
        <a href="tel:+14709700798" class="btn btn-secondary">470 970 0798</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="arm-footer" id="footer-area">
    <p><strong>ACED Pixels</strong> — Creative & Visual</p>
    <p>Part of <a href="/">ACED Division LLC</a> · <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    <p style="margin-top:0.8rem;">© 2026 ACED Division LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
 
